    "description": "Senshukai Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the mail order, corporate, and insurance businesses in Japan. The company conducts mail order sales through catalogs and the Internet. It also operates Belle Maison net, a general online shopping site for various products, including fashion, interior, and Disney goods; Belle Maison catalogs; Belle Maison store; Monthly Club, a shopping style that delivers Belle Maison products on a regular basis; ihana.com, an online shopping site for flowers and gifts; gift catalogues; and TSUNAGU SENSHUKAI, a gift shop. In addition, the company provides Senshukai childcare, which operates nurseries and after-school care centers; Belle Maison life plan design; Belle Maison home staging, business support and sales promotion; and clothes and bedding cleaning services. Further, it provides points accumulation and purchase, insurance, and credit card services. Senshukai Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1946 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
